decoDesc.decoNote:
Nomina sacra; names of the donors (or owners);
incipit of prayers and hymns (sometimes only one word); 
some other words (or their abbreviation), e.g., salām (e.g., fol. 51v), la-ṭǝbuʿ (e.g., fol. 52v), ʾafṭunä (e.g., fol. 33v); elements of the punctuation signs and the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.
